reviewText: This is a strange TV series that doesn't really come to anything of substance.  There are three young women who share an apartment.  They long to be celebrities and try to behave like the celebrities they read about, thinking that is how they will achieve their goals.  It doesn't work, of course.  No one else appears in the show, only those three, and they you never see them outside the apartment, which creates a kind of a claustrophobic feel to the show.
